    • getPartResults

      public void getPartResults(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent enterpressed) throws IOException
      This method searches a table for any items that have string of characters or a number that the user has inputted. It compares the user input to names of the parts or the ID number of a part. If the search box is empty, the table loads all values.
      Throws:
      IOException

    • getProductResults

      public void getProductResults()
      This method searches a table for any items that have string of characters or a number that the user has inputted. It compares the user input to names of the products or the ID number of a product. If the search box is empty, the table loads all values.
